name: CerebrovascularDiseaseDiagnosisSCT
title: Cerebrovascular Disease Diagnosis SCT
description: This value set may undergo changes until the HL7 Multiple Chronic Care FHIR IG is formally published in 2024.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains SNOMED CT diagnosis terms representing cerebrovascular disease.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this set of values is to identify patients who have a diagnosis of cerebrovascular disease.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes the SNOMED CT cerebrovascular disease diagnosis concepts.),(Exclusion Criteria: None)
